                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-270-off1405 t18310630-270-cd1406"></join>, 1 crown, 1 half-crown, 20 shillings, and 8 sixpences, the monies of 
                     <persName id="t18310630-270-victim1941" type="victimName">
                        Philip 
